title: 494-Joey Diaz-Your Mom's House with Christina P and Tom Segura
description:
What can we say? The DOCTA is in! All time favorite of the show, the one and only Joey "Coco" Diaz AKA Mad Flavors World is down to spit game like no one else. Honestly, we're in the room but we're just along for the ride.

No one has stories or can get away with more than our Uncle Joey. 

Pull your jeans up and get ready to laugh your nuts off. Every Joey appearance is an instant classic.
